OL,3,CRNLI saved 355 lives in 2023 as
OL,4,Ccharity launches fundraising campaign
OL,6,FThe Royal National Lifeboat
OL,7,FInstitution (RNLI) has revealed its
OL,8,Fcrews and lifeguards saved 355 lives
OL,9,Fin 2023, as the charity launched a
OL,10,Ffundraising campaign in its 200th year.
OL,12,FIts lifeboats were launched 9,192
OL,13,Ftimes last year across the UK and
OL,14,FIreland, making it the RNLI's second-
OL,15,Fbusiest year of the past decade,
OL,16,Faccording to its rescue figures.
OL,18,FThe charity has urged members of the
OL,19,Fpublic to take part in its Mayday Mile
OL,20,Fcampaign to raise money by covering a
OL,21,Fmile a day during the month of May.
