OL,6,FRNLI lifeboat crews saved the lives of
OL,7,F269 people over the course of 2023,
OL,8,Fwhilst the charity's beach lifeguards
OL,9,Fsaved 86 lives.
OL,11,FThe number of lives saved includes
OL,12,Fthose of migrants attempting to cross
OL,13,Fthe Channel when the RNLI has been
OL,14,Ftasked by HM Coastguard to go to the
OL,15,Faid of small, unseaworthy boats.
OL,17,FThe busiest lifeboat stations last
OL,18,Fyear were Poole, Plymouth and
OL,19,FEastbourne.
