OL,6,FAlex Hodson, who was rescued by Conwy
OL,7,FRNLI in September 2022, said he
OL,8,F"wouldn't have survived" without the
OL,9,Flifeboat's crew.
OL,11,FMr Hodson, from Eccleshall,
OL,12,FStaffordshire, said: "It was such a
OL,13,Fcalm and beautiful day, but when we
OL,14,Fturned around we realised we were
OL,15,Fsurrounded by water, and the current
OL,16,Fwas so strong that I couldn't swim
OL,17,Fagainst it.
OL,19,F"We could see the beach, but we just
OL,20,Fcouldn't get there ` we were very
OL,21,Fscared.
