OL,6,FLast month, the Archbishop of
OL,7,FCanterbury praised RNLI staff as
OL,8,F"models for everyone" who "risk their
OL,9,Flives for those who are not known to
OL,10,Fthem" as the charity celebrated its
OL,11,F200th anniversary at a thanksgiving
OL,12,Fservice at Westminster Abbey.
OL,14,FThe RNLI's crews and lifeguards have
OL,15,Fsaved more than 144,000 lives since
OL,16,Fits formation in 1824 and its
OL,17,Fvolunteers provide a 24-hour search
OL,18,Fand rescue service around the coasts
OL,19,Fof the UK and Ireland.
